story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA added an event.
message:
Are you curious about the concept of Wakanda? Do you want to know more about afrofuturism, afropolitanism, the intricacies in the relationship between Africa and its diaspora? Or do you just want to talk about your impressions of the movie "Black Panther"? Look no farther! We’ve brought together experts in these fields to show you da wae.
Food will be served!!!
